name: MEDITATION
description:
There comes a time when trying to focus on something, we will find that the biggest distraction is our own thoughts. Overthinking. Ranging from simple things (tasks, works, relations) to the complex things (fictional stories, problem that doesn't exist, dream). Meditation will help us find our way back to our original selves, reduce anxiety and improve our brain performance.

5000x5000 px
500 dpi
230 unique doodle characters
